{"tid":1860444,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】露械警告!! Poly狗公借TG文宣group呃蝦條","createTime":"2020-02-03T15:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T04:13:17.000Z","uid":124178,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb68c479dd3e3983e640710f73e2cf9332ea2c2","tid":1860444,"uid":124178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:57:29.000Z","msg":"由於件事實在好On9，小弟決定係度同大家分享下以此為鑒<br />\n<br />\n事源前幾日，小弟有個女仔friend係Telegram俾個唔識嘅人dm𢯎計傾。由於個friend嘅telegram只係用黎睇文宣而非做交友用，平時唔會亂咁俾人知，同埋佢問埋身邊啲人都唔知條友係邊個，所以除咗公海group都應該唔會俾人加到。<br />\n<br />\n咁個friend都唔係啲乜善男信女，無啦啦俾人dm咁就梗係陪佢玩下睇佢乜料。一開波條友話傾淫嘢，傾傾下又話互send相咁，佢就send咗張自己嘅背影圖，個friend就求其係網上搵啲相俾佢。之後條友開始話想對住啲相打丁。 嚟一刻，個friend發覺嚟個係一個試探佢嘅大好機會，於是扮唔識乜係DIY話叫佢教下🤔<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\nDNLM佢真係send佢碌尻過黎🤦<br />\n<br />\n個friend收到碌尻個陣完全係呆咗，即刻係啲friend group講翻發生乜事問應該點算。咁小弟作為一個盡責嘅好朋友，覺得對於嚟啲人要俾佢一個深刻嘅教訓💪 <br />\n<br />\nPS：對話內容有彩蛋喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/a/ucvapaB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FucvapaB&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdAfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=93984002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/a/ucvapaB</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8c92b2cfb7ecefd4ecb862e99ff6c2b7c19f6f","tid":1860444,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"條J短到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317fff2e309d646810681d270e52f49ced0c85f0","tid":1860444,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:01:08.000Z","msg":"Load唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434edbadf34554f654647d6e10588a11fe6d400d","tid":1860444,"uid":49018,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:01:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咁撚短都夠膽腥畀人睇"},{"pid":"21199c839ddb99e383a82b69c7b39a9